meta.about: This json file contains metadata for every Magic: the Gathering set as of October 3, 2021. Specifically, it contains Set Code, Set Name, Release Date, and number of cards (optional). It is used to supplement the SetList.json file from mtgJSON (Found here: https://mtgjson.com/file-models/setlist/) because it is missing data for some obscure sets. This data was scraped from deckstats.net (URL: https://deckstats.net/sets/?lng=en).
